&gt; I am not very knowledgeable on electronics but I have been looking for a group I can discuss some psychic phenomena. I would openly discuss it here but I do not want to distract the focus of the group.  perhaps I can explain my weirdness to the people who are in the GCP group or one of the sites. I could here too, if it doesn&#39;t bother anyone.
